179
00:32:58.025 --> 00:32:59.692
Ha ucciso mamma!

180
00:33:14.423 --> 00:33:15.173
Aria?

181
00:33:19.272 --> 00:33:21.072
Tuo padre ti sta cercando?

182
00:33:21.192 --> 00:33:22.842
