207
00:35:39.649 --> 00:35:40.299
Ok?

208
00:35:41.837 --> 00:35:42.967
Ho paura!

209
00:35:43.087 --> 00:35:44.867
Lo so. Va bene.

210
00:35:46.219 --> 00:35:47.619
Puoi stare con me.

211
00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:50.260
Non ti mandero' via.

212
00:35:52.106 --> 00:35:52.756
Ok?

213
00:35:53.896 --> 00:35:56.046
Non ti mandero' da nessuna parte.

214
00:36:13.328 --> 00:36:15.327
E' li' fuori da una settimana
circa.


215
00:36:15.447 --> 00:36:16.978
Se torno dove ho ucciso
sua madre,


216
00:36:17.098 --> 00:36:19.098
